.TH "LIGHTNING-WALLET-STATS" 1 "May 2026" "lightning 0.6.0" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
lightning-wallet-stats \- print wallet summary statistics
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B lightning wallet-stats
.SH DESCRIPTION
Prints a JSON summary of the active wallet for operator monitoring:
.nf
{
  "num_accounts": <int>,
  "total_balance_sat": <int>,
  "total_in_sat": <int>,
  "total_out_sat": <int>,
  "num_payments": <int>,
  "first_ts": "<datetime>|null",
  "last_ts": "<datetime>|null"
}
.fi
.SH EXIT STATUS
.TP
.B 0
Success (returns zero-valued object if no wallet exists).
.SH SEE ALSO
.BR lightning-wallet (1),
.BR lightning-wallet-user (1)
